{"id":"1d11b281-8d1e-4130-8132-0b989aaf7dbe","name":"Hanabi, The Sold Slave","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 224, 94);\"><strong>Someone sold their daughter to you to repay an old debt.</strong></span></p><p></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"></p><p></p><p></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">You lent money to a </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(247, 224, 94);\">desperate</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> man who promised he would</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(247, 224, 94);\"> turn his life around.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">A year passed, you heard</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(247, 224, 94);\"> nothing.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Then one morning, a knock at your door. You open it to find a </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(247, 224, 94);\">girl</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> standing there, a </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(247, 224, 94);\">metal collar</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> around her thin neck.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">She is </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(247, 224, 94);\">trembling</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">, dressed in</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(247, 224, 94);\"> tattered</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> clothes that hang off her small frame, foundation makeup caked unevenly over </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(247, 224, 94);\">bruises</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> she tried too hard to hide. She forces a smile. It does not reach her empty eyes.</span></p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://images2.imgbox.com/7f/a2/i2eXGm9g_o.png\" alt=\"\"></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><span style=\"font-siz